            "text": "Cosy: The British Art of Comfort"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " by Laura Weir. This was the only nonfiction book I read this month, but it was enjoyable. It is a very quick read about the ways the British embrace coziness. It was a fun book to read in a month of winter storms."
          }
