              }
            ],
            "text": "Activity"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " - Celebrating Daniel's birthday! While it wasn't the best month for a birthday, we tried to make it special with scattered celebrations throughout the month. His birthday was the weekend that the snowstorm started, so many things were canceled or postponed. We had Franklin's BBQ at home as a family, went to Hestia for date night, and let Carson pick out a present - a \"Daddy Shark\" t-shirt and chocolates."
          }
        ]
