            "type": "text",
            "text": "(3) The boys did another fun visit to Gramma & Grampa's house."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(4) Caden still loves his bath time. Love this cheesy face!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
            "attrs": {
