              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(1) Caden did his first trip to the grocery store in February! He was in awe of all the sights and sounds."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(2) We switched Carson into a toddler bed in February. He loves it and is doing really well at nighttime. I've kissed daytime naps goodbye, but we do still have a \"rest time\" at home in his room."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(3) On Daniel's actual birthday, we did what we could by making a yummy cake and giving him gifts. Even though we were snowed in, we tried to make it special day for him."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(4) I had fun plans for Carson and Caden to wear their cute new Valentine's shirts to, but with the snowstorm, we settled for wearing them at home for a photo shoot."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
            "attrs": {
