              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(1) & (4) The next couple days after Valentine's Day brought the most snow! These are not sights I thought I'd ever see out my window in Texas!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(2) & (3) We tried to get out and have fun in the snow, but the boys were not a huge fan. Carson especially disliked it after falling face first in it!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
            "attrs": {
              "src": "images/SFTM_February-2021_EverydayAccountsBlog.com_4.png",
